Just a let down but this is good. Finally some good tv

summary: “Sandra Oh pushed so hard for my part to not be another white british actress. And the director and everyone was like 'Sandra,...
body:
“Sandra Oh pushed so hard for my part to not be another white british actress. And the director and everyone was like ‘Sandra, we need to move on, we need to start shooting’ and Sandra was like 'No. Keep auditioning the brits in L.A, we need to see everybody. We need to see everyone.”

KIRBY HOWELL BAPTISTE
